          <h1 class="title">2018 Undergraduate Open Days</h1>
          <nav class="primary-nav">
            <span class="nav-title">School Events<i class="nav-toggle"></i></span>
            <div class="nav-links">
              <a href="/events/2018-02-02-avds-assessment-days" class="nav-link">Applicant Visit Days and Assessment Days commence</a>
              <a href="/events/2018-02-02-ug-openday" class="nav-link">2018 Undergraduate Open Days</a>
              <a href="/events/01-02-2018-pg-openday" class="nav-link">Postgraduate Open Day - March 2018</a>
            </div>
          </nav>
          <div class="feed-entry">
  <div class="meta">
    <span>
      <a href="http://www.cs.bham.ac.uk/events/2018-02-02-ug-openday">
        <i class="fa fa-link"></i>
        Permalink
      </a>
    </span>
    <span>Published: Fri 2nd February 2018</span>
  </div>
  <article>
    <p>The University will be hosting our next <a href="http://www.birmingham.ac.uk/undergraduate/visit/opendays/">Undergraduate Open Days</a> on Friday 22nd and Saturday 23rd June 2018.</p>

<p>The School of Computer Science will be giving talks, manning stands, performing tours and showing demonstrations.</p>

<p>Sign up here:</p>

<p><a href="https://bham.hobsonsradius.com/ssc/iform/G0TC0rx7A7020x671c0xK.ssc">UG Open Day</a></p>

<p>In the meantime, if you have any questions please free free to join our <a href="https://www.facebook.com/groups/UoBCSUGApplicants2018/">UG Applicant Facebook Group</a>. It's run by the Admissions Team and current students, who will be happy to answer any questions you might have.</p>

<p><br/></p>

<hr/>

<p><br/></p>

<p>Computer Science UG Admissions<br />
